$ CSS properties

Some CSS properties include
  • → development/web/CSS/properties/background[`background-*`]
  • → development/web/CSS/properties/border[`border`]
  • `box-*` properties, especially `→ development/web/CSS/properties/box/sizing` which controls how a box's total width and height is calculated.
  • `→ development/web/CSS/properties/clear`
  • → development/web/CSS/properties/column/count[`column-count`]
  • → development/web/CSS/properties/content[`content`]
  • → development/web/CSS/properties/display[`display`]
  • → development/web/CSS/properties/flex[`flex-*`]
  • → development/web/CSS/properties/float[`float`]
  • → development/web/CSS/properties/font-family[`font-family`]
  • → development/web/CSS/properties/font/size[`font-size`]
  • `font-style` (which can be set to `italic`)
  • `font-weight` (which might be set to `bold` etc.)
  • → development/web/CSS/properties/list-style[`list-style*`]
  • → development/web/CSS/properties/margin[`margin`]
  • → development/web/CSS/properties/object/fit[`object-fit`]
  • → development/web/CSS/properties/orphans-widows[`orphans` and `widows`] specify the minum number of lines in a block container that must be shown at the bottom/top of a page, region or column.
  • → development/web/CSS/properties/overflow[`overflow`] specifies what happens if an element's content does not fit within the boundaries of the element.
  • → development/web/CSS/properties/page-break[`page-break-before`, `page-break-after` and `page-break-inside`] control how and when a new page is started when a document is printed.
  • → development/web/CSS/properties/position[`position`]
  • → development/web/CSS/properties/text/transform[`text-transform`]
  • → development/web/CSS/properties/top-right-bottom-left[`top`, `right`, `bottom` and `left`].
  • → development/web/CSS/properties/transform[`transform-*`]
  • → development/web/CSS/properties/translate[`translate`]
  • → development/web/CSS/properties/transition[`transition-*`]
  • → development/web/CSS/properties/vertical-align[`vertical-align`]
  • → development/web/CSS/properties/visibility[`visibility`]
  • `→ development/web/CSS/properties/white-space`
  • `→ development/web/CSS/properties/writing-mode`

